cardinalr05trian.Rmd
library(cardinalR)
library(langevitour)
train_3d_data <- traingular_3d_with_noise(sample_size = 512, num_noise_dims = 2, 
                         min_noise = -0.05, max_noise = 0.05)

colnames(train_3d_data) <- paste0("x", 1:NCOL(train_3d_data))

langevitour(train_3d_data, pointSize = 2)
train_data <- triangular_plane_with_bkg_noise(sample_size = 675, num_noise_dims = 2, 
                                min_noise = -0.05, max_noise = 0.05)

colnames(train_data) <- paste0("x", 1:NCOL(train_data))

langevitour(train_data, pointSize = 2)
